headline: Partnering for AI Visibility: Notified CEO Erik Carlson with Profound CEO James Cadwallader, Live at Nasdaq
summary: Tech Edge hosted a fireside chat on August 12 at Nasdaq MarketSite with Erik Carlson, President and Chief Executive Officer at Notified and James Cadwallader, Chief Executive Officer and Co-founder of Profound. The in-person interview was joined by Editor-in-Chief John Jannarone and they discussed Notified’s newly-announced partnership with Profound that will help clients optimize press releases […]
